The computer would needs following capabilities 
# natural language processing to communicate successfully in a human language;
# knowledge representation to store what it knows or hears;
# automated reasoning to answer questions and to draw new conclusions;
# machine learning to adapt to new circumstances and to detect and extrapolate patterns.

# Acting humanaly - Turing Test
# Thinking humanaly - Cognitive model approach.
# Thinking Rationally - Laws of thought approach inline with logic.
# Acting Rationally - The rational agent approach, which is an agent acting to achieve the best expected outcome. 
